      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY ARNOLD (8) did a good job to finish second last time out over 520m at this track (30.46) in a Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. HARD SNIFF STYLE (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.66) at this track behind Currency Keeping in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. DOLLAR KEEPING (4) finished well back at this track last time when a 9 length sixth (30.59) but recorded second best time of the card when winning five back. Should be in this for a long way. WELL READ (5) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
